  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This award strives to support the establishment of a sound private, well-functioning, equitable financial sector that fulfills critical roles in a market economy. More specifically, this includes The project supports the tax administration, Direc&#xE7;&#xE3;o-geral de Contribui&#xE7;&#xF5;es e Impostos (DGCI), in streamlining and documenting audit procedures, and providing training on use of procedures. Additional activities for 2017 include implementing withholding and corporate tax return forms and accompanying instructions, developing a sales tax return form, and implementing the ministerial order on withholding of property tax.. The project supports the tax administration, Direc&#xE7;&#xE3;o-geral de Contribui&#xE7;&#xF5;es e Impostos (DGCI), in streamlining and documenting audit procedures, providing training on use of procedures, and improving basic management practices. Additional activities for 2017 include implementing withholding and corporate tax return forms and accompanying instructions, developing a sales tax return form, and implementing the ministerial order on withholding of property tax.. Project is closed.</narrative>
  </description>
